comments: Lopez (MIL) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
McDaniels (PHI) initiates contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that affects his ability to get to the pass.
Harden (PHI) loses control of the ball on his own and legally continues his dribble.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) slightly extends his arms into McDaniels (PHI) as he releases to the basket but the contact is marginal.
Embiid (PHI) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) layup attempt.
Middleton (MIL) moves forward into Maxey (PHI) and dislodges him from his position.
Niang (PHI) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot.
Middleton (MIL) initiates contact to Harden (PHI) that causes him to lose his balance.
Embiid (PHI) initiates contact to Antetokounmpo (MIL) that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Allen (MIL) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Allen (MIL) gathers the ball and legally takes two steps before jumping to make the pass.
